resources.string: BiREXA© is self-breast examination guide intended to help women do breast examination.\n\nBiREXA© is not a substitute for professional medical consultation and is not offering diagonsis or treatment of any illness.

1.دفع قيمة قسيمة الحجز فقط مقابل 1500 جنيه مصرى .

2. سجل كود القسيمة عند اقرب معمل مسجل لدينا تحت بند أقرب معمل ماموجرام.

3. استلم نتيجة الماموجرام من خلال التطبيق او من خلال المعمل لاستلام نسخه ورقيه.

Mother or sister with breast cancer < 50 years.
Relatives with ovarian cancer.
Presence of Breast cancer gene BRCA1 and BRCA2.
Higher risk if age is above 50.
Early menstrual period before 12.
Late menopause after 55.
No pregnancy or late delivery after 30.
Physical inactivity increases breast cancer risk.
Being overweight increases breast cancer risk.
Using combination hormone therapy.
Previous history of breast cancer.
Previous treatment using radiation therapy.
Drinking alcohol.
